{"id":44,"title":"问：什么是RAG机制（Retrieval-Augmented Generation）？它试图解决大模型的什么问题？","slug":"问：什么是RAG机制（Retrieval-Augmented-Generation）？它试图解决大模型的什么问题？-1766595047","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：RAG是“检索增强生成”的缩写，指在大语言模型生成回答时，引入外部检索的相关信息作为辅助。【简单理解】LLM有时会出现“幻觉”（hallucination）问题，即编造出不存在的事实。为减少这类错误，RAG在模型作答时先根据问题到知识库**中检索相关材料，将检索结果与提示一起提供给模型，促使模型基于真实资料生成答案。这样一来，模型的回答有据可依，大幅提升准确性和可信度。RAG机制常用于**闭环问答**、**文档对话**等场景：例如用户问一个专业问题，系统先从数据库检索资料段落，再把这些资料附加到prompt里让大模型参考，生成包含资料内容的回答。总结来说，RAG结合了信息检索和文本生成的优点，**缓解了大模型知识有限和胡编乱造的缺点**，提供更可靠的回答。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:47.298626+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:47.298626+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-803d-aa8d-e5652adb0f7d","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":44,"blog_post_id":44,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.602566+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.602566+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:47.298626+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:47.298626+08:00"}